OL,3,CMan admits 'brutal' murder of
OL,4,Cpartner's mother and attempting to
OL,5,Ckill girlfriend
OL,7,FA 50-year-old man has pleaded guilty
OL,8,Fto the "brutal and horrific" murder of
OL,9,Fhis partner's mother and the attempted
OL,10,Fmurder of his partner.
OL,12,FDamian Homer, appearing by videolink
OL,13,Ffrom HMP Hewell, was told he faces a
OL,14,Fmandatory life sentence after
OL,15,Fadmitting both charges at Worcester
OL,16,FCrown Court.
