OL,4,Cpartner's mother and attempting to
OL,5,Ckill girlfriend
OL,7,FNo details of the offences were opened
OL,8,Fto the court by prosecutor Harpreet
OL,9,FSandhu KC after Homer, of Haresfield
OL,10,FClose, Worcester, pleaded guilty to
OL,11,Fthe murder of Wendy Francis, 61, and
OL,12,Fattempting to murder her daughter
OL,13,FStacey Hill, 38.
OL,15,FBoth women were attacked on March 2
OL,16,Fthis year, with emergency services
OL,17,Fbeing called to the Haresfield Close
OL,18,Faddress at about 8.30pm.
