OL,7,F"Homer launched a brutal knife attack
OL,8,Fon Wendy and another woman, aged 38,
OL,9,Fat a house on Haresfield Close in
OL,10,FWorcester following an argument", West
OL,11,FMercia Police confirmed.
OL,13,FThe force added: "Wendy, who was his
OL,14,Fgirlfriend's mum, sadly died at the
OL,15,Fscene. The 38-year-old woman was
OL,16,Fseriously injured but thankfully
OL,17,Fsurvived."
