OL,7,FAdjourning the case to a date to be
OL,8,Ffixed, Judge Rupert Mayo told the
OL,9,Fcourt: "I am not going to sentence
OL,10,Ftoday ` there are two main reasons.
OL,12,F"The first is the defendant should be
OL,13,Fhere."
OL,15,F"This was a horrific and brutal knife
OL,16,Fattack"
