OL,7,FJudge Mayo adds: "I am not prepared to
OL,8,Fpass sentence for an offence as grave
OL,9,Fas this on the videolink. However
OL,10,Fexpedient that might be, it's wrong.
OL,11,FHe (Homer) needs to be here.
OL,13,F"Secondly, I am told the psychiatric
OL,14,Freport has only recently been made
OL,15,Favailable."
OL,17,FAddressing Homer directly, the judge
OL,18,Fadded: "I will be sentencing you at
OL,19,Fsome stage between now and the 27th of
OL,20,FAugust.
